    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/276377ef67d188e08258b23990a5a8ca.poster.avif?t=1754947907\" width=426 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/276377ef67d188e08258b23990a5a8ca.webm?t=1754947907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/276377ef67d188e08258b23990a5a8ca.mp4?t=1754947907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Twisted Screens</strong> invites you to step into the  boots of Tessa Gracelyn, a mercenary hired by ATR Industries to explore a long-abandoned science facility — one now overrun with horrifying experiments to shut down their nuclear reactor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teaming up with <strong>Legsy-0</strong>, a sarcastic A.I. assistant from ATR’s golden age, you’ll navigate the metal halls through a mix of parkour and puzzles. Legsy’s sharp wit and questionable guidance will either help you survive. or make you go insane.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/c0cd7d350ff3960a012639186dcf4b73.poster.avif?t=1754947907\" width=426 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/c0cd7d350ff3960a012639186dcf4b73.webm?t=1754947907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/c0cd7d350ff3960a012639186dcf4b73.mp4?t=1754947907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first-person sci-fi adventure inspired by the Mascot Horror genre, you’ll leap, climb, and sprint through puzzle-filled environments, uncover absurd lore, and make use of strange gadgets to progress. The world is twisted, the humor is questionable. welcome to ATR Industries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
